snippet.title: Tetraphobia Kickstarter Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Tetraphobia is a twin stick roguelite set in a world of floating isles. Fight alongside Trixx, Reno and Benny as you battle through a procedurally generated world with fully destructible environments.

Fight against a host of unique enemies and uncover whether there's any substance behind the fear of the four.

Follow me to keep up with all the updates:
